{"prompt": "Design a professional portfolio for a UI/UX designer. The aesthetic should incorporate a clean charcoal grey.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>UI/UX Designer Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #36454F; /* Charcoal Grey */\n            --secondary-color: #4F5B66; /* Slightly lighter charcoal */\n            --accent-color: #FFFFFF; /* White for contrast */\n            --text-color: #E0E0E0; /* Light grey for text */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #about h2, #portfolio h2, #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        .project-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .project-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .project-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n        }\n\n        .project-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .project-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .project-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .project-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .project-info a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .project-info a:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n        }\n\n        #contact input,\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        #contact input::placeholder,\n        #contact textarea::placeholder {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            opacity: 0.7;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Jane Doe</h1>\n            <p>UI/UX Designer | Problem Solver | Visual Storyteller</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <p>Passionate UI/UX designer with a keen eye for detail and a user-centered approach. I transform complex ideas into intuitive and visually appealing digital experiences. My process involves thorough research, wireframing, prototyping, and iterative testing to ensure the best possible user journey.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>My Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"project-grid\">\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/36454F/FFFFFF?text=Project+Image+1\" alt=\"Project 1 Thumbnail\">\n                    <div class=\"project-info\">\n                        <h3>E-commerce Redesign</h3>\n                        <p>Revamped a legacy e-commerce platform to improve conversion rates and user engagement.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#project1\">View Case Study</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/36454F/FFFFFF?text=Project+Image+2\" alt=\"Project 2 Thumbnail\">\n                    <div class=\"project-info\">\n                        <h3>Mobile App UI Kit</h3>\n                        <p>Designed a comprehensive UI kit for a new productivity mobile application.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#project2\">View Case Study</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/36454F/FFFFFF?text=Project+Image+3\" alt=\"Project 3 Thumbnail\">\n                    <div class=\"project-info\">\n                        <h3>SaaS Dashboard</h3>\n                        <p>Created an intuitive and data-rich dashboard for a B2B SaaS product.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#project3\">View Case Study</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Jane Doe. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic form submission simulation (replace with actual backend integration)\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! I will get back to you soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}